import React,{Component} from 'react';
import {
  Container,
  Nav,
  Navbar,
  Form,
  FormControl,
  Button,
  Row,
  Col
}from "react-bootstrap";
class App extends Component {
  render() {
    return(
      <Container>
        <Navbar bg="dark" variant="dark">
          <Row>
            <Col xs={8}>
              <Navbar.Brand style={{colo:"white"}} href="/">Akses Sport</Navbar.Brand>
              <Nav>
                <Nav.Item>
                  <Nav.Link style={{color:"grey"}} href="/">Berita</Nav.Link>
                </Nav.Item>
                <Nav.Item >
                  <Nav.Link style={{color:"grey"}} href="/">Live Score</Nav.Link>
                </Nav.Item>
                <Nav.Item>
                  <Nav.Link style={{color:"grey"}} href="/">Home
                  </Nav.Link>
                </Nav.Item>
                <Nav.Item>
                  <Nav.Link style={{color:"grey"}} href="/">Transfer Pemain</Nav.Link>
                </Nav.Item>
                <Nav.Item>
                  <Nav.Link style={{color:"grey"}} href="/">Tim</Nav.Link>
                </Nav.Item>
              </Nav>
            </Col>
            <Col xs={2}></Col>
            <Col xs={4}>
              <Form inline>
                <FormControl type="text" placeholder="Silahkan Cari" />
              </Form>
              <Button variant="outline-info">Search</Button>
            </Col>
          </Row>
        </Navbar>
      </Container>
    );
  }
}


export default App;
